There's a reason for that.

00:45:46.390 --> 00:45:47.690
Hi.

00:45:47.690 --> 00:45:51.490
&gt;&gt; Is it a stressful
or a happy progress

00:45:51.490 --> 00:45:54.030
when you're making the comics?

00:45:54.030 --> 00:45:55.330 position:56%
