my hand gets tired.

00:46:01.550 --> 00:46:03.080
That's one of the most
stressful parts.

00:46:03.080 --> 00:46:05.960
And also, sometimes, if I'm trying
to like think of how a story ends

00:46:05.960 --> 00:46:08.880
and I can't do it, I'm just like,
oh no, what am I going to do?

00:46:08.880 --> 00:46:12.520
But then, you know, you
run of time and you just go

00:46:12.520 --> 00:46:15.270
with whatever comes
up in your brain.

00:46:15.270 --> 00:46:16.570
&gt;&gt; Hi.

